	         <a name="features"></a>
        <h2 class="divider">Features</h2>

        <p>Create and share your own data into an Open Data site using the workflows you already know. New styling is available, customize and create your own site in minutes.</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Enable Open Data on your Organization and Groups</li>
			<li>Federated searching across Organizations and groups</li>
			<li>Simple workflows for sharing your data</li>
			<li>Support for spatial and non-spatial tables</li>
			<li>Interactive filters to explore data</li>
			<li>Share links to filtered views of datasets</li>
		</ul>
         <p>&nbsp;</p>
        <div class="clear"></div>
		<a name="dataRequirements"></a>
        <h2 class="divider">Data requirements</h2>
        <p>ArcGIS Open Data currently works with Features from Hosted Feature Serivces as well as Feature and Map Services from an ArcGIS Server.</p>

        <p>&nbsp;</p>

