        <h2 class="divider">What's new</h2>
		<p>Open Data .beta was released in April 2014 and we have since added the follow to our final release:</p>
		
		<ul>
			<li>Support for tables</li>
			<li>Simple charting of datasets</li>
			<li>Full data downloads</li>
			<li>Swiss ninja something</li>
			<li>opendata.arcgis.com has been released!</li>
		</ul>

